<title>Chanchin Pha</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Zie khawvel damlai lungngaih meipi zing nuoi ahin,
 Gitlohna leh lungngaihna ten ei tuom velin;
 Ka Hukdampa'n ei lungsietna,
 Chanchin pha thu ka hun zakin;
 Ka lungkhamna cheng cheng,
 Nawpna a suok zotai.

[V2]
 Chanchin hawih kei di'n nawpna,
 Chanchin pha kei di'n damna;
 Lalpa thuthiem lopi pen ahi,
 Aw Kei din damna.

[V3]
 2. Gitloh huihpi leh zinmangin ei um vel mahleu,
 Ei Hukdampan A lungsietna kulhpi sungah;
 Ka thagau liem puilut intin,
 Ka tanpa thutiem dettak chu;
 A lungsietna lien chu bang ma'n, a nang zo puoi.

[V4]
 3. A lungsietna min lopi mai chu kei din a lul,
 Kei gilo, liengvai, gimthei hing hawilo cha hih;
 Kumsawt pielgal kawt ei hawnsak,
 A thisan lul thiengtho tak chun;
 Lunggil in ei muhsak in aw, ka Lal Isu.</lyrics>
</song>